<bibRefCitation id="0A644B38132AFF997FED771260BBFBBC" author="Desutter-Grandcolas" box="[941,1260,1124,1149]" pageId="9" pageNumber="407" refString="Desutter-Grandcolas, L. (1993) Luzarida Hebard, 1928 et genres affines: genres nouveaux, phylogenie et scenarios (Orthoptera, Grylloidea, Phalangopsidae, Luzarinae). Revue francaise d'Entomologie, 15, 169 - 182." type="journal article" year="1993">
